Installation:
-------------
 -> apt install i3, i3blocks, i3lock
 -> apt install xfce4-terminal, zsh # basic terminal setup
 -> apt install sxiv, feh # image viewer & background display control
 -> apt install pulseaudio, pulseaudio-utils, pavucontrol # audio control
 -> apt install scrot, imagemagick, xautolock # screen lock
 -> xfce4-powermanager # for laptop power management
 -> apt install network-manager # network service manager
 -> apt install thunar # file manager
 -> apt install xfce4-notifyd # Notification service

Additionally:
-------------
enable screen lock script
chmod +x ~/.config/i3/scripts/lock
